OL,3,CCCTV captures thieves breaking into
OL,4,Chome leaving couple 'afraid and
OL,5,Cvulnerable'
OL,7,FA couple felt afraid and vulnerable in
OL,8,Ftheir own home after two men ransacked
OL,9,Ftheir house and stole precious
OL,10,Fjewellery worth tens of thousands of
OL,11,Fpounds.
OL,13,FThe thieves were caught on CCTV
OL,14,Fbreaking into Sharon and Kevin Mills'
OL,15,Fhome in Auckley late on the 18 August.
OL,17,FShortly after 11pm, camera footage
OL,18,Fcaptured two hooded men, with a ladder
OL,19,Fin tow, arriving at the home they've
OL,20,Flived in for 40 years.
