OL,7,FThey had ripped out the alarm system
OL,8,Fand smashed through the front door.
OL,10,FThey didn't leave a drawer unopened in
OL,11,Ftheir search for things to steal,
OL,12,Fleaving with a collection of family
OL,13,Fjewellery, including Sharon's mums
OL,14,Fwedding ring.
OL,16,FHer mum had lived with them four years
OL,17,Fago until her death.
