OL,7,FSharon said, "I get insecure, these
OL,8,Fpeople know who you are, but they
OL,9,Fdon't know who you are and it's not a
OL,10,Fnice feeling.
OL,12,F"Some of the things she left, they had
OL,13,Fbeen in that and that's what I can't
OL,14,Fcope with. I just thank God that
OL,15,Fnobody were hurt."
OL,17,FThe men returned just an hour later to
OL,18,Ftake two vehicles - a car and a work
OL,19,Fvan. The van was later found abandoned.
