OL,8,FNational Statistics show from the year
OL,9,Fto March, the residential burglary
OL,10,Frate in England was 7.5 per 1000
OL,11,Fhousehold.
OL,13,FIn Yorkshire and the Humber the rate
OL,14,Fwas 10.6, but in South Yorkshire, it's
OL,15,Falmost double the England average, at
